icipate in a hearing telephonically or electronically. In a Section concerning scavenger sales, requires certain county collectors to publish notice of the intended application for judgment and sale of all properties upon which all or a part of the general taxes for each of 3 or more years (instead of 2 or more years) are delinquent.", "versions": [{"url": "http://ilga.gov/legislation/fulltext.asp?DocName=09700HB4044&GA=97&SessionId=84&DocTypeId=HB&LegID=63281&DocNum=4044&GAID=11&Session=&print=true", "doc_id": "ILD00051668", "name": "Introduced"}], "type": ["bill"], "id": "ILB00021300", "bill_id": "HB 4044"}